reviews.text: One of the SHITTEST place to eat..Food is disgusting. The dumpling noodle I ordered has dumpling that has frozen filling, raw noodle and a lukewarm soup base...And to make it worse, I told the waitress and she said they are too busy now to give me a replacement but to come back in 2 hours as it will be after the peak hours...I still have to fxxking pay for an inedible bowl of noodle and they know full well that I won't redeem the raincheck...

food are nice and speical, and I tried double-dimpling noodle, its nice! It also claimed dun add MSG to the food, which I think is true... when u search for good food with low cost. this is a good choice. but rmb this is not a high class restaurant, still have room to imrpove the environment
